summary:
Hello Taylor and Swifties!
No one is going to see this but I just wanted to say hi - I’m new to the online fandom having been...
body:
Hello Taylor and Swifties!

No one is going to see this but I just wanted to say hi - I’m new to the online fandom having been lurking for a while… All the new videos and gifs of the tour and Taylor looking so happy made me so over-excited I had to make an account 😬

I’ve been a fan since 2010 when my friend introduced me to her music, and I’m finally going to see Taylor live in just under a month!!

I’m keen to make friends so please send me a message if you want to - especially if you’re going to the show in London on the 22nd! ✨

@taylorswift
